  <!-- Introducción de la actividad -->  
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="narrative-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>This Number Talk encourages students to rely on their knowledge of multiplication, place value, and properties of operations to mentally solve division problems. The reasoning elicited here helps to develop students' fluency with multiplication and division within 100.</p>
<p>To find the quotients of larger numbers, students need to look for and make use of structure in quotients that are smaller or more familiar, or to rely on the relationship between multiplication and division (MP7).</p>
  </paragraphs>

